reviews.review_text:
Shall we go… Gotta laugh wrote out a review that my I phone swallowed whole.
So I guess I will just go with
I like the moment at the end of the night
Where Bobby says, ‘goodnight’
And Garcia seems to take everyone
Including the band by surprise by starting the vocals into WBYG…
Best of 73
Best..
50 years later and a surprise AUD... Proof we're just never gonna hear it all.
